# Project Explanation: Redemption & Marketplace Module

## 📋 **API Endpoints List**

### **Admin Panel APIs** (`/api/admin/panel`)
1. `GET /dashboard/summary` - Get dashboard statistics
2. `GET /reports` - Generate redemption reports (daily/monthly/user-wise)
3. `GET /export/redemptions` - Export redemptions to CSV

### **Approval System APIs** (`/api/approval`)
1. `GET /pending` - Get pending approvals
2. `GET /stats` - Get approval statistics
3. `GET /search` - Search approvals
4. `GET /:approvalId` - Get approval details
5. `PUT /:approvalId/process` - Process approval (approve/reject/escalate)
6. `GET /:approvalId/audit-logs` - Get audit logs
7. `POST /bulk-process` - Bulk process approvals

### **Marketplace APIs** (`/api/marketplace`)
#### Public Routes:
1. `GET /products` - Get product listings
2. `GET /products/:asinSku` - Get product by ASIN/SKU
3. `GET /categories` - Get categories
4. `GET /rewards/physical` - Get physical rewards

#### Protected User Routes:
5. `POST /wishlist/add` - Add to wishlist
6. `DELETE /wishlist/remove` - Remove from wishlist
7. `GET /wishlist` - Get wishlist
8. `POST /cart/add` - Add to cart
9. `PUT /cart/update` - Update cart item
10. `DELETE /cart/remove` - Remove from cart
11. `GET /cart` - Get cart
12. `DELETE /cart/clear` - Clear cart
13. `POST /orders/place` - Place order
14. `GET /orders` - Get user orders
15. `GET /orders/:orderId` - Get order details
16. `POST /rewards/physical/redeem` - Redeem physical reward
17. `GET /rewards/physical/redemptions` - Get physical redemptions
18. `POST /tickets` - Create support ticket
19. `GET /tickets` - Get user tickets

#### Admin Routes:
20. `PUT /admin/orders/:orderId/status` - Update order status
21. `PUT /admin/rewards/physical/:redemptionId/approve` - Approve physical redemption
22. `PUT /admin/rewards/physical/:redemptionId/status` - Update redemption status
23. `PUT /admin/tickets/:ticketId/status` - Update ticket status

### **Marketplace Upload APIs** (`/api/marketplace/admin`)
1. `POST /upload/products` - Upload products CSV

## 🗄️ **Database Tables Structure**

### **Core Tables:**
1. **`users`** - Main user table
2. **`redemptions`** - All redemption records
3. **`redemption_channels`** - Redemption methods (UPI, Bank, etc.)
4. **`redemption_statuses`** - Redemption status tracking

### **Amazon Marketplace Tables:**
5. **`amazon_marketplace_products`** - Amazon product catalog
6. **`user_amazon_wishlist`** - User wishlist items
7. **`user_amazon_cart`** - User shopping cart
8. **`user_amazon_orders`** - Amazon orders
9. **`amazon_order_items`** - Order line items
10. **`amazon_tickets`** - Support tickets

### **Physical Rewards Tables:**
11. **`physical_rewards_catalogue`** - Non-Amazon physical items
12. **`physical_rewards_redemptions`** - Physical reward redemptions

### **Approval System Tables:**
13. **`redemption_thresholds`** - Approval threshold rules
14. **`redemption_approvals`** - Approval queue
15. **`approval_roles`** - Admin approval roles
16. **`user_approval_roles`** - User-role mapping
17. **`approval_audit_logs`** - Approval audit trail

## 🔗 **Database Connectivity**

### **Users ↔ Marketplace Flow:**
```
users (id)
    ↓ (1:1)
retailers (userId) / electricians (userId) / counter_sales (userId)
    ↓
redemptions (userId)
    ↓ (1:Many)
user_amazon_orders (userId)
    ↓ (1:Many)
amazon_order_items (orderId)
    ↓ (1:Many)
amazon_tickets (userId, orderId)
```

### **Users ↔ Redemptions Flow:**
```
users (id)
    ↓ (1:Many)
redemptions (userId)
    ↓ (1:1)
redemption_approvals (redemptionId, userId)
    ↓ (1:Many)
approval_audit_logs (approvalId, redemptionId)
```

### **Users ↔ Physical Rewards:**
```
users (id)
    ↓ (1:Many)
physical_rewards_redemptions (userId)
    ↓ (Many:1)
physical_rewards_catalogue (rewardId)
```

