## 🚀 **How It Works**

### **Redemption Process:**
```
User requests redemption
    ↓
Check user points balance
    ↓
Check approval thresholds
    ↓
Auto-approve / Flag for approval
    ↓
If flagged → Add to approval queue
    ↓
Admin reviews & approves/rejects
    ↓
Process payment/shipment
    ↓
Update user points & status
```

### **Marketplace Order Process:**
```
User adds items to cart
    ↓
Place order with points
    ↓
Check inventory availability
    ↓
Create redemption request
    ↓
If approved → Update inventory
    ↓
Process order/shipping
    ↓
Track delivery
```

