## 🔄 **Workflow Examples**

### **Example 1: User redeems Amazon product**
```typescript
// 1. User adds product to cart
POST /api/marketplace/cart/add
{ "asinSku": "B08N5WRWNW", "quantity": 1 }

// 2. User places order
POST /api/marketplace/orders/place
{
  "userId": 123,
  "items": [...],
  "shippingAddress": {...}
}

// 3. System creates redemption
// 4. System checks approval rules
// 5. Admin approves (if needed)
PUT /api/approval/{approvalId}/process
{ "action": "APPROVE" }

// 6. Order processed, points deducted
```

### **Example 2: Admin bulk approves**
```typescript
// 1. Admin views pending requests
GET /api/approval/pending

// 2. Admin selects multiple
POST /api/approval/bulk-process
{
  "approvalIds": [1, 2, 3],
  "action": "APPROVE",
  "reason": "Bulk approval for weekend"
}

// 3. System processes all in transaction
```

This system provides a complete e-commerce redemption platform integrated with a robust approval workflow, suitable for B2B loyalty programs with complex business rules.